<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 09:14:09 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国和欧盟就即将实施的电动汽车关税举行技术会谈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-eu-held-technical-talks-impending-ev-tariffs-2024-07-04/</link><description>中国商务部在例行新闻发布会上表示，中国和欧洲就中国电动汽车关税问题举行了多轮技术谈判，欧盟委员会将于周四确认这一消息。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 08:41:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-eu-held-technical-talks-impending-ev-tariffs-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>由于美国利率前景和科技股上涨，亚洲股市吸引了强劲的外资流入</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/asian-stocks-draw-robust-foreign-inflows-us-rate-outlook-tech-rally-2024-07-04/</link><description>经过两个月的抛售后，外国投资者在 6 月份将大量资金投入亚洲股市，因为美国物价压力的缓解引发了人们对美联储今年降息的希望。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 08:37:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/asian-stocks-draw-robust-foreign-inflows-us-rate-outlook-tech-rally-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉汽车首次进入中国政府采购清单</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-cars-first-time-chinese-government-purchase-list-2024-07-04/</link><description>据中国官方媒体澎湃新闻周四报道，特斯拉最畅销的 Model Y 被列入中国地方政府可以购买作为服务车的电动和插电式混合动力车型清单。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 08:17:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-cars-first-time-chinese-government-purchase-list-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>习近平和普京阐述了欧亚安全俱乐部的雄心</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/xi-putin-set-out-ambitions-eurasian-security-club-2024-07-04/</link><description>中国国家主席习近平周四敦促地区安全俱乐部成员抵制外部干预，而俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京(Vladimir Putin)将在该组织的年度会议上谈到建立新的欧亚安全体系。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 07:34:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/xi-putin-set-out-ambitions-eurasian-security-club-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国习近平敦促地区安全集团抵制“外部干涉”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-xi-urges-regional-security-bloc-resist-external-interference-2024-07-04/</link><description>中国国家主席习近平对包括俄罗斯及其最新成员国白俄罗斯在内的地区经济、国防和安全集团表示，成员国必须共同努力抵制“外部干涉”并坚定地相互支持。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 07:16:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-xi-urges-regional-security-bloc-resist-external-interference-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国警告长期热浪可能损害水稻和棉花作物</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-warns-prolonged-heatwave-may-damage-rice-cotton-crops-2024-07-04/</link><description>中国气象局周四警告说，7月份中国东部、中部和南部地区的长期热浪天气可能会影响水稻和棉花的生产，因为极端天气继续威胁着中国的粮食生产。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 07:12:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-warns-prolonged-heatwave-may-damage-rice-cotton-crops-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国中金公司着眼于东南亚扩张以缓解国内困境</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/chinas-cicc-eyes-southeast-asia-expansion-bid-ease-domestic-woes-2024-07-04/</link><description>中国国际金融公司（中金公司）投资银行业务负责人表示，由于国内交易量下滑损害了其前景，中金公司计划通过在印度尼西亚和马来西亚等国开设办事处来扩大其在东南亚的业务。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 06:53:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/chinas-cicc-eyes-southeast-asia-expansion-bid-ease-domestic-woes-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>中印外长同意尽早解决边界问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/india-china-foreign-ministers-agree-step-up-talks-border-issues-2024-07-04/</link><description>新德里在一份声明中表示，印度外交部长苏杰生周四在哈萨克斯坦会见了中国外长王毅，两人同意加紧谈判，尽早解决边境问题。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 06:02:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/india-china-foreign-ministers-agree-step-up-talks-border-issues-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>早恋：中国的犬类婚礼呈上升趋势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/puppy-love-canine-weddings-rise-china-2024-07-04/</link><description>这是一场梦幻般的婚礼，拥有风景如画的户外环境、白色蕾丝礼服和美味的蛋糕。对于金毛猎犬布莉和邦德来说，这是在它们最亲密的人类和犬类朋友面前喜结连理的完美日子。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 05:16:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/puppy-love-canine-weddings-rise-china-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：美国降息、英国政治动荡的押注增多</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-07-04/</link><description>韦恩·科尔 (Wayne Cole) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 04:47:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国习近平在电动汽车关税生效前向欧盟理事会主席致意</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-greets-eu-council-president-ahead-ev-tariffs-taking-effect-2024-07-04/</link><description>中国官方媒体称，中国国家主席习近平周四致电即将上任的欧洲理事会主席安东尼奥·科斯塔，表示祝贺，此时距离欧盟委员会对中国电动汽车的限制计划生效几个小时。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 04:21:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-greets-eu-council-president-ahead-ev-tariffs-taking-effect-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾总统下令缓和南海局势，军事参谋长表示</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-president-orders-de-escalation-south-china-sea-military-chief-says-2024-07-04/</link><description>菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯周四表示，在与中国因在有争议的浅滩上为菲律宾军队补给的任务发生冲突后，菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯已命令其武装部队缓和南海的紧张局势。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 04:17:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-president-orders-de-escalation-south-china-sea-military-chief-says-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国比亚迪在泰国开设电动汽车工厂，这是东南亚首家电动汽车工厂</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-opens-ev-factory-thailand-first-southeast-asia-2024-07-04/</link><description>中国比亚迪周四在泰国开设了一家电动汽车工厂，这是该汽车制造商在东南亚的第一家工厂，东南亚是一个快速增长的区域电动汽车市场，比亚迪已成为该市场的主导者。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 04:00:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-opens-ev-factory-thailand-first-southeast-asia-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>随着气候变化加剧，中国警告将出现更热、更长时间的热浪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-weather-authority-warns-high-summer-temperatures-2024-07-04/</link><description>气象局周四警告说，由于气候变化，中国正面临更炎热、持续时间更长的热浪，以及更频繁和不可预测的暴雨，世界第二大经济体正准备迎接另一个炎热的夏季。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 03:55:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-weather-authority-warns-high-summer-temperatures-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>新西兰提议对南极洲进行较小规模的基地重建</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/antarctica-new-zealand-proposes-smaller-redevelopment-base-2024-07-04/</link><description>政府机构周四表示，新西兰已经提出了一项新的、规模较小的重建该国南极洲基地的提案，此前一项计划因预算超支而暂停。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 03:45:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/antarctica-new-zealand-proposes-smaller-redevelopment-base-2024-07-04/</guid></item></channel></rss>